  "detailed_description": "Trash horror game with underworld monsters that were unleashed when three friends broke the spell protecting their neighborhood.<br>The mess changed the reality of the world of the 3 young people who will now have the mission to defeat the creatures, to imprison them again.<br><br>Search every corner of the map in search of the crystals that are keys to other dimensions and face guardians possessed by the spell of the underworld who guard pieces of the relic capable of fixing the mess.<br><br>Reality is scrambled and things are out of place, just as memories intertwine, the unexplainable can come true.<br><br><strong>They made a mess, you'll have to clean it up.</strong><br>Live the experience of shooting fireworks, magic bombs and using an enchanted broom to defeat monsters from the underworld in third person.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262580/extras/db51885bf23c3cb708e83a815f875b40.avif?t=1711469549\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262580/extras_big/db51885bf23c3cb708e83a815f875b40.avif?t=1711469549 width=800 height=448 /></span><br><br><strong>The Clown is the nightmare of many. </strong><br>Escape until the time is right to send you back to the depths of the underworld.<br><br><strong>The barrier of Sanity has been breached.</strong><br>Explore houses that mix illusions, nightmares and memories in a confusing reality for our heroes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262580/extras/31b48aea9de3f3b54d9bff701db326bf.avif?t=1711469549\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262580/extras_big/31b48aea9de3f3b54d9bff701db326bf.avif?t=1711469549 width=800 height=448 /></span><br><br><strong>The guardians of the underworld are possessed.</strong> <br>Battle each guardian in your territory, defeat them and gather every part of the relic that will be able to close the passage with the non-human world again.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262580/extras/8e06f467c8fb3161f6d67ba8374842ae.avif?t=1711469549\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262580/extras_big/8e06f467c8fb3161f6d67ba8374842ae.avif?t=1711469549 width=800 height=448 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262580/extras/88f6d066df3d21b0b6491d52bf9b48fd.avif?t=1711469549\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262580/extras_big/88f6d066df3d21b0b6491d52bf9b48fd.avif?t=1711469549 width=800 height=448 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Trash horror game with underworld monsters that were unleashed when three friends broke the spell protecting their neighborhood.<br>The mess changed the reality of the world of the 3 young people who will now have the mission to defeat the creatures, to imprison them again.<br><br>Search every corner of the map in search of the crystals that are keys to other dimensions and face guardians possessed by the spell of the underworld who guard pieces of the relic capable of fixing the mess.<br><br>Reality is scrambled and things are out of place, just as memories intertwine, the unexplainable can come true.<br><br><strong>They made a mess, you'll have to clean it up.</strong><br>Live the experience of shooting fireworks, magic bombs and using an enchanted broom to defeat monsters from the underworld in third person.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262580/extras/db51885bf23c3cb708e83a815f875b40.avif?t=1711469549\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262580/extras_big/db51885bf23c3cb708e83a815f875b40.avif?t=1711469549 width=800 height=448 /></span><br><br><strong>The Clown is the nightmare of many. </strong><br>Escape until the time is right to send you back to the depths of the underworld.<br><br><strong>The barrier of Sanity has been breached.</strong><br>Explore houses that mix illusions, nightmares and memories in a confusing reality for our heroes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262580/extras/31b48aea9de3f3b54d9bff701db326bf.avif?t=1711469549\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262580/extras_big/31b48aea9de3f3b54d9bff701db326bf.avif?t=1711469549 width=800 height=448 /></span><br><br><strong>The guardians of the underworld are possessed.</strong> <br>Battle each guardian in your territory, defeat them and gather every part of the relic that will be able to close the passage with the non-human world again.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262580/extras/8e06f467c8fb3161f6d67ba8374842ae.avif?t=1711469549\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262580/extras_big/8e06f467c8fb3161f6d67ba8374842ae.avif?t=1711469549 width=800 height=448 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262580/extras/88f6d066df3d21b0b6491d52bf9b48fd.avif?t=1711469549\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262580/extras_big/88f6d066df3d21b0b6491d52bf9b48fd.avif?t=1711469549 width=800 height=448 /></span>",
